		<node ID="ID_1707892641" LINK="https://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Introduction_to_Information_Technology/Web_Technologies" TEXT="Introduction to Information Technology/Web Technologies ">
			<node ID="ID_418325465" TEXT="Introduction []. In order to make websites look and function a certain way web developers utilize different languages. The three core languages that make up the World Wide Web are HTML CSS and JavaScript." />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1208042976" LINK="http://csis.pace.edu/lixin/download/lab-introduce-web.pdf" TEXT="Introduction to Web Technologies - Seidenberg School of ">
			<node ID="ID_930067342" TEXT="Introduction to Web Technologies  &#8226; Use HTML form and the HTTP protocol to send requests and data to web applications and download HTML documents; &#8226; Maintain cookies (name value pairs explained later) deposited on client computers by a web  The web server is mainly for receiving document requests and data submission from web browsers" />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_12396995" LINK="http://www.alphadevx.com/a/7-The-Basics-of-Web-Technologies" TEXT="The Basics of Web Technologies - alphadevx.com">
			<node ID="ID_391465999" TEXT="The Basics of Web Technologies; Published at 2001-07-13 10:24:48 by John Collins . Introduction. Web technologies is a general term referring to the many languages and multimedia packages that are used in conjunction with one another to produce dynamic web sites such as this one. Each separate technology is fairly limited on its own and " />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1257105216" LINK="https://www.slideshare.net/vikramsingh.v85/introduction-to-web-technology" TEXT="introduction to web technology - SlideShare">
			<node ID="ID_1871433276" TEXT="An Introduction to Web Technologies Vikram Singh Asst. Professor Department of IT JECRC Jodhpur Slideshare uses cookies to improve functionality and performance and to provide you with relevant advertising." />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1994350128" LINK="https://study.com/academy/lesson/what-is-web-technology-definition-trends.html" TEXT="What is Web Technology? - Definition  Trends - Video ">
			<node ID="ID_1291605472" TEXT="The methods by which computers communicate with each other through the use of markup languages and multimedia packages is known as web technology. In the past few decades web technology has " />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_848936712" LINK="https://sites.google.com/site/basicphptutorial/introduction-to-web-technology-html-basic-tags-css-table-and-forms" TEXT="Introduction to Web Technology HTML Basic Tags CSS ">
			<node ID="ID_256536504" TEXT="Introduction to Web Technology HTML Basic Tags CSS Table and Forms. CSS Basic. JavaScript. MYSQL. PHP. Sitemap. Introduction to Web Technology HTML Basic Tags CSS Table and Forms. What is an HTML File? HTML stands for Hyper Text Markup Language ; An HTML file is a text file containing small markup tags;" />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1877564961" LINK="https://www.coursera.org/learn/web-development" TEXT="Introduction to Web Development | Coursera">
			<node ID="ID_1291295605" TEXT="Learn Introduction to Web Development from University of California Davis. This course is designed to start you on a path toward future studies in web development and design no matter how little experience or technical knowledge you currently " />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1069331473" LINK="https://www.scss.tcd.ie/owen.conlan/CS7062/1_Web_Technologies_Handout.pdf" TEXT="www.scss.tcd.ie">
			<node ID="ID_981243656" TEXT="www.scss.tcd.ie" />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1114379552" LINK="https://www.studytonight.com/servlet/introduction-to-web.php" TEXT="Introduction to Web | Servlet Tutorial | Studytonight">
			<node ID="ID_212517776" TEXT="Servlet: Introduction to Web. Web consists of billions of clients and server connected through wires and wireless networks. The web clients make requests to web server. The web server receives the request finds the resources and return the response to the client. When a server answers a request it usually sends some type of content to the client." />
			</node>
		<node ID="ID_1108708824" LINK="https://tms-outsource.com/blog/posts/web-technologies/" TEXT="9 Web Technologies Every Web Developer Must Know in 2020 | TMS">
			<node ID="ID_1047250048" TEXT="We present you with an introduction to web technologies and the latest web technologies list hoping it will make things at least a bit easier for you. Now let&#8217;s take a look. What is Web Technology? You have probably heard the term &#8220;web development technologies&#8221; before but did you ever think about what it actually means?" />
			</node>
