			<node ID="ID_773652368" TEXT="Here&#8217;s a custom exception handler example to configure for &#8220;java.lang.Exception&#8221; so that it&#8217;s called for any exception thrown by Action. To create a custom exception handler you need to subclass &#8220;org.apache.struts.action.ExceptionHandler&#8221; and override the execute method. MyCustomExceptionHandler.java" />
